snippet.title: MINDHACK Early Access Date Trailer
snippet.description:
MINDHACK is a visual novel where the player turns evildoers' minds into a flower garden.
You’re a genius hacker who can penetrate and destroy other peoples minds.
Hack into the brain of various dangerous prisoners
and rewrite their personalities to make them as candid as a cute sheep.
Enjoy the pleasure of mental destruction.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1727210/MINDHACK/?
Twitter: https://twitter.com/VODKA_demo
